title: New Wave Remixes Mixed Vol. 5 by Technics2000
description:
Got a little lazy with this one and just took songs from each of the vols. so far. Direct download links will be available at Http://Technics2000.Wordpress.com 

New Wave Remixes Mixed Vol. 5 - Technics2000 
MPEG-1 layer 3 
192kbit (CBR) 
44100Hz Joint Stereo 

01. Howard Jones - Things Can Only Get Better (Stan Kolev Dub Tribal Mix) 
02. Howard Jones - Things Can Only Get Better (Chico Secci Hurricane Mix) 
03. Tears for Fears - Everybody Wants to Rule this World (The Chosen Few Extended Mix) 
04. Simple Minds - Don&#039;t You Forget About Me (Peter Rauhofer Mix)

06. Cetu Javu - Situations (MOS Leg Mix) 
07. Echo and the Bunnymen - The Killing Moon (T-Rek&#039;s Desert Disco Dub Mix) 
08. Depeche Mode - Shake the Disease (Tiga Mix) 
09. Depeche Mode - Enjoy the Silence (Tekara Mix) 
10. When in Rome - The Promise (Coliseum Mix)

12. Celebrate the Nun - Will You Be There (Razormaid Mix) 
13. Electronic - Getting Away With It (Electronic Mix) 
14. Anything Box - Living In Oblivion (Razormaid Mix)
